{"id":"5e9bfefd774c2610387e43be","artists":["5e9b68e07a1236eccfeb1ef2"],"title":"Premiere: Chris Cookson – Sophia","content":"<p>Having impressed with his debut single, Pillow Talk, towards the latter stages of 2014, London’s <strong>Chris Cookson</strong> is back with his second offering, the beautifully melodic<em> Sophia</em>.</p><p> Again showcasing a knack for penning a killer hook, alongside an addictive, memorable chorus, it’s drenched in nostalgia and a sense of yearning for love and days gone by. Mixing modern R&B style inspirations, with the sort of electronic production usually associated with the likes of SOHN or Chet Faker, it’s a diverse sound, whilst remaining inherently pop at heart. Check it out below, alongside Pillow Talk.</p>\n<p><iframe src=\"https://w.soundcloud.com/player/?url=https%3A//api.soundcloud.com/tracks/191765400&auto_play=false&hide_related=false&show_comments=true&show_user=true&show_reposts=false&visual=true\" width=\"100%\" height=\"450\" frameborder=\"no\" scrolling=\"no\"></iframe></p>\n<p><iframe src=\"https://w.soundcloud.com/player/?url=https%3A//api.soundcloud.com/tracks/177673970&auto_play=false&hide_related=false&show_comments=true&show_user=true&show_reposts=false&visual=true\" width=\"100%\" height=\"450\" frameborder=\"no\" scrolling=\"no\"></iframe></p>\n","slug":"30918-premiere-chris-cookson-sophia","category":"music","date":1424271197000,"wpid":30918,"isSticky":false,"featured_image":{"width":100,"height":100,"src":"2015/02/11001005_10155270159330574_1125197808_o-100x100.jpg","placeholder":"data:image/jpeg;base64, "},"createdAt":1587281661464,"updatedAt":1588403510905,"author":"5e9b68b27a1236eccfeb1d27","old_image":"2015/02/11001005_10155270159330574_1125197808_o-100x100.jpg","categories":["music","new"]}